	• Windows can automate tasks
		○ done through unattended windows setup utility 
			§ automates mass deployment on windows
			§ utilizes config files that contain credentials ie admin password
			§ if unattended windows setup config files are left after installation they can reveal credentails
	• unattended windows setup
		○ uses on of the follow files that contain account info
			§ C:\Windows\Panther\Unattend.xml
			§ C:\Windows\Panther\autounattend.xml
    ○ passwords encoded in base64
